DOC.brief_summary: Pharmacokinetic properties, safety and tolerability of RGB-10 and Forsteo will be compared in healthy female volunteers.
DOC.brief_title: A Study Aimed at Assessing the Pharmacokinetic Properties of RGB-10 and Forsteo
DOC.criteria: Healthy adult female subjects 1855 years of age (inclusive) BMI must be between 18.5 and 27 kg/m2 (inclusive)
